---
layout: templates/documentation.njk
title: Lab
permalink: lab/index.html
eleventyNavigation:
  key: Lab
description: Experimental workspace for rapid prototyping and creative coding experiments
---

<section class="prose prose-lg max-w-4xl">
  <header class="mb-8">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Lab: Experimental Workspace</h1>
    <p class="text-xl text-base-content/80 leading-relaxed">
      The Lab is your creative playground for rapid prototyping, animation experiments, and design explorations. 
      This landing page serves as the hub for accessing all experimental projects and provides quick guidance for creating new ones.
    </p>
  </header>

  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-12">
    <div class="card bg-base-200 shadow-lg">
      <div class="card-body">
        <h2 class="card-title text-2xl">🚀 Quick Start</h2>
        <p>Ready to experiment? Creating a new lab page is simple:</p>
        <ol class="list-decimal list-inside space-y-2 text-sm">
          <li>Create a <code>.njk</code> file in <code>njk/_pages/lab/</code></li>
          <li>Add frontmatter with <code>parent: Lab</code></li>
          <li>Start experimenting!</li>
        </ol>
        <p class="text-sm text-base-content/70 mt-4">
          ✨ <strong>Navigation automatically updates</strong> - your page appears in the Lab dropdown menu instantly.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card bg-base-200 shadow-lg">
      <div class="card-body">
        <h2 class="card-title text-2xl">🛠️ Available Tools</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm">
          <li><strong>GSAP Animation Suite</strong> - Professional animation library</li>
          <li><strong>Design System</strong> - Figma-synced tokens & components</li>
          <li><strong>Tailwind CSS</strong> - Utility-first styling framework</li>
          <li><strong>External Libraries</strong> - Easy CDN integration</li>
          <li><strong>Custom Assets</strong> - Page-specific CSS & JavaScript</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="mb-12">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Current Experiments</h2>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      
      <div class="card bg-gradient-to-br from-primary/10 to-secondary/10 border border-primary/20 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
        <div class="card-body">
          <h3 class="card-title text-lg">
            <a href="/lab/text-party/" class="link link-hover">Text Party</a>
          </h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-base-content/70">
            Font morphing animations using OpenType.js and GSAP MorphSVG. Watch text transform between different typefaces with smooth vector interpolation.
          </p>
          <div class="card-actions justify-end mt-4">
            <div class="badge badge-primary badge-sm">Text Effects</div>
            <div class="badge badge-secondary badge-sm">GSAP</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/10 to-neutral/10 border border-accent/20 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
        <div class="card-body">
          <h3 class="card-title text-lg">
            <a href="/lab/text-radial-stagger/" class="link link-hover">Text Radial Stagger</a>
          </h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-base-content/70">
            Radial text animation patterns with GSAP SplitText. Characters animate in circular formations with staggered timing effects.
          </p>
          <div class="card-actions justify-end mt-4">
            <div class="badge badge-accent badge-sm">Animation</div>
            <div class="badge badge-neutral badge-sm">SplitText</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card bg-gradient-to-br from-success/10 to-warning/10 border border-success/20 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
        <div class="card-body">
          <h3 class="card-title text-lg">
            <a href="/lab/text-to-vector/" class="link link-hover">Text to Vector</a>
          </h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-base-content/70">
            Converting typography to SVG paths for advanced text manipulation and morphing effects. Explore vector-based text animations.
          </p>
          <div class="card-actions justify-end mt-4">
            <div class="badge badge-success badge-sm">SVG</div>
            <div class="badge badge-warning badge-sm">Typography</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card bg-gradient-to-br from-info/10 to-primary/10 border border-info/20 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
        <div class="card-body">
          <h3 class="card-title text-lg">
            <a href="/lab/blockframes/" class="link link-hover">Blockframes</a>
          </h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-base-content/70">
            SVG-based frame animations and transitions. Explore geometric patterns and structured animation sequences.
          </p>
          <div class="card-actions justify-end mt-4">
            <div class="badge badge-info badge-sm">SVG</div>
            <div class="badge badge-primary badge-sm">Frames</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card bg-gradient-to-br from-secondary/10 to-accent/10 border border-secondary/20 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
        <div class="card-body">
          <h3 class="card-title text-lg">
            <a href="/lab/printmarks/" class="link link-hover">Print Marks</a>
          </h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-base-content/70">
            CSS print styling experiments and print-specific design patterns. Explore print media queries and layout techniques.
          </p>
          <div class="card-actions justify-end mt-4">
            <div class="badge badge-secondary badge-sm">CSS</div>
            <div class="badge badge-accent badge-sm">Print</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card bg-gradient-to-br from-warning/10 to-error/10 border border-warning/20 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
        <div class="card-body">
          <h3 class="card-title text-lg">
            <a href="/lab/text-masking/" class="link link-hover">Text Masking</a>
          </h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-base-content/70">
            Advanced CSS masking techniques applied to typography. Create complex text reveal effects and layered compositions.
          </p>
          <div class="card-actions justify-end mt-4">
            <div class="badge badge-warning badge-sm">CSS</div>
            <div class="badge badge-error badge-sm">Masking</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="mb-12">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 text-white">Developer Quick Reference</h2>
    
    <div class="collapse collapse-arrow bg-base-200 mb-4">
      <input type="radio" name="quick-ref-accordion" checked="checked" /> 
      <div class="collapse-title text-xl font-medium">
        📝 Frontmatter Template
      </div>
      <div class="collapse-content"> 
        <div class="mockup-code">
          <pre><code>---
layout: templates/documentation.njk
title: Your Experiment Name
description: Brief description of your experiment
eleventyNavigation:
  key: Your Experiment Name
  parent: Lab  # REQUIRED for navigation
scripts: >  # Optional: External libraries
  &lt;script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/p5.js/1.4.0/p5.min.js">&lt;/script>
styles: >  # Optional: Custom CSS
  &lt;style>
    .experiment-container { background: #000; }
  &lt;/style>
---</code></pre>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="collapse collapse-arrow bg-base-200 mb-4">
      <input type="radio" name="quick-ref-accordion" /> 
      <div class="collapse-title text-xl font-medium">
        🎨 GSAP Integration
      </div>
      <div class="collapse-content"> 
        <div class="mockup-code">
            <pre><code>&lt;script type="module">
          import { gsap } from 'https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/gsap/3.13.0/gsap.min.js';
          import { ScrollTrigger } from 'https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/gsap/3.13.0/ScrollTrigger.min.js';
          import { MorphSVGPlugin } from 'https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/gsap/3.13.0/MorphSVGPlugin.min.js';
  
  // Your animation code here
  gsap.from('.element', { duration: 2, y: 100, opacity: 0 });
&lt;/script></code></pre>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="collapse collapse-arrow bg-base-200 mb-4">
      <input type="radio" name="quick-ref-accordion" /> 
      <div class="collapse-title text-xl font-medium">
        🧩 Component Usage
      </div>
      <div class="collapse-content"> 
        <div class="mockup-code">
          <pre><code>{%raw%}{% include "atoms/button/button.njk" with {
  text: "Run Experiment",
  variant: "primary"
} %}

{% include "organisms/section/title.njk" with {
  title: "Experiment Results",
  subtitle: "Interactive demonstration"
} %}{%endraw%}</code></pre>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </section>

