    <div>
      <h3 class="font-bold">Need more details?</h3>
      <p>Check the comprehensive <a href="https://github.com/datainkio/portfolio/blob/text-animations/njk/_pages/lab/README.md" class="link">Lab README</a> for complete documentation, troubleshooting guides, and advanced techniques.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

</section>